Basic steps:
    Its a simple scaffhold for posts
    Setup up your db by running rake db:create and rake db:migrate.
    Run the app and see the way new post can be created and deleted

What we want you to code ?
    Write Integration test using Webrat + Selenium

What will be evaluated ?
    Clean code
    Ability to test the posts index action
    Ability to test the posts destroy action with javascript alert
    Ability to test the "New Post" facebox popup
    Ability to test the "check title availability" link_to_remote with result text assertion

